citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 1:10 p.m. on
01-APR-19.
Upon arrival at the facility contact was made with the licensee's spouse. She stated that the licensee was not home
and would not return for several more hours. I then left the facility.
End of report.
